- ts-convergent-polypharmacology: All 6 developer tasks completed. Full pipeline implemented in src/bioagentics/tourettes/convergent_polypharmacology/ (6 scripts, 01-06).
- Phase 1a (#965): Mapped 238 ChEMBL compounds to 11 convergent pathways. 4/11 druggable, 7 druggability gaps. 230 drugs cover >=1 pathway.
